Soccer writer Vuyokazi Nkanjeni has been shortlisted in a national competition for journalists Picture: Vuyokazi Nkanjeni / Facebook The Herald and Weekend Post soccer writer Vuyokazi Nkanjeni is one of only three journalists to have made the national gsport Awards Woman in Print short-list and now she needs your help to bring home the award. Readers can show their support for Vuyokazi by registering and voting for her to win on gsport.co.za/voting. Once registered, click on the Woman in Print category where her name will appear. Entries close on August 7. The winners will be announced on August 26. Keep track of all the latest by following #gsport12 and @gsport4girls. Share on Facebook Share Share on Twitter Tweet Share on Google Plus Share